<plot>Hidden away in the barren wasteland of California's Mojave Desert is the region's last fresh water source, a natural spa. A shrinking retirement community have made their home here. Only those over seventy years of age are granted entry and the only mode of transport is by golf-cart. They call it the Fountain of Youth.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?201409</url></doc>
